900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA3845-3.html</guid></item><item><title>中国人口老龄化及其对中国安全的影响</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_briefs/RBA3372-1.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/research_briefs/RBA3372-1/_jcr_content/par/teaser_copy.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1773352314899.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;本文简要回顾了兰德公司对中国人口趋势的研究，并探讨了这些趋势可能如何影响该国的安全和经济增长。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_briefs/RBA3372-1.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普退休账户提案的影响：6300 万替代退休计划的潜在成本和节省...</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_briefs/RBA4392-2.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/research_briefs/RBA4392-2/_jcr_content/par/teaser.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1773321968708.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普总统在 2026 年国情咨文演讲中介绍了特朗普退休账户 (TRA)。本简报对 TRA 进行了一年、十年和四十年的成本分析，并提供了对其政策影响的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_briefs/RBA4392-2.html</guid></item></channel></rss>